useful helper scripts for all purposes see the documentation in each file for
usage

for installation, invoke the script install_nesono-bin from the nesono-bin
directory or...

add the following lines to your ~/.profile (when checked out to ~/nesono-bin)

# the nesono script directory
if [ -d ~/nesono-bin ]; then
  export PATH=$PATH:~/nesono-bin
fi

# and copy or link inputrc and vimrc
copy:
cp ~/nesono-bin/inputrc ~/
cp ~/nesono-bin/vimrc   ~/

link:
ln -s ~/nesono-bin/inputrc ~/.inputrc
ln -s ~/nesono-bin/vimrc   ~/.vimrc
